---
title: Contact Sorry :(
description: Contact Sorry to talk about what you need help with or to say hi
---
.container-inner
  %h1 Contact Sorry
  %h2 We are currently available for select projects
  %p
    We’d love hear from you. Reach out and let us know what you need help with or just say hello
    = image_tag 'wave.png', width: '14px', class: 'wave'
  .clearfix
    %form{'accept-charset' => 'UTF-8', action: 'https://formspree.io/carter@sorry.is', method: 'POST'}
      .form-item
        %input{name: 'name', placeholder: 'Your name', required: true}
      .form-item
        %input{name: 'name', type: 'email', placeholder: 'Your email', required: true}
      .form-item
        %select{name: 'budget', required: true}
          %option{ selected: true, disabled: true } Your budget
          %option $25,000 - $50,000
          %option $50,000 - $100,000
          %option $100,001+
      .form-item
        %textarea{name: 'message', placeholder: 'Tell us about what you\'re working on', required: true}
      %input{type: 'hidden', name: 'utf8', value: '✓', class: 'button'}
      .form-item
        %button{type: 'submit'} Send
        / %p We'll get back to you within 48 hours.
    %ul.no-style
      %li New Clients: #{link_to 'business@sorry.is', 'mailto:business@sorry.is'}
      %li Careers: #{link_to 'apply@sorry.is', 'mailto:apply@sorry.is'}
      %li General Inquiries: #{link_to 'hi@sorry.is', 'mailto:hi@sorry.is'}
  %h3 based in Santa Monica, CA
%script{src: 'https://api.tiles.mapbox.com/mapbox-gl-js/v0.13.1/mapbox-gl.js'}
:javascript
  var url = window.location.href;
  var captured = /thanks=([^&]+)/.exec(url)[1];
  var result = captured ? captured : 'myDefaultValue';
